title: Trabant Houseplant Sale with UD Botanic Gardens - University of Delaware
text:
About this Event
Trabant University Center, University of Delaware, Newark, DE 19711, USA
Join us at the Trabant sale for a wide selection of houseplants, ranging from vibrant foliage to exotic succulents and everything in between. Whether you're looking to brighten up your dorm room, office, or home windowsill, we have the perfect plants for you. Our knowledgeable UD Botanic Gardens staff and dedicated volunteers will be on hand to assist you with any questions, offer care tips, and help you choose the best plants for your environment. This is a fantastic opportunity to bring nature indoors as the weather cools down and to learn more about houseplant care.
